@startuml

skinparam backgroundColor white
skinparam defaultFontSize 12
skinparam ArrowColor #2C3E50
skinparam ArrowThickness 2
skinparam RectangleBorderColor #2C3E50
skinparam RectangleFontSize 13

title Types of Uses Relationships

rectangle "**Module A**" as A #D5E8D4

rectangle "Required\nDependency" as R #FFCDD2
rectangle "Conditional\nDependency" as C #FFF9C4
rectangle "Optional\nDependency" as O #E3F2FD

A -down-> R : <<required uses>>\nA cannot function without R
A -down-> C : <<conditional uses>>\nA uses C in some configurations
A -down-> O : <<optional uses>>\nA degrades gracefully without O

note right of R
  **Mandatory**
  Must always be present
end note

note right of C
  **Configurable**
  Present in some
  deployments
end note

note right of O
  **Enhancing**
  Improves A but
  not essential
end note

legend bottom
  |= Strength |= Description |
  | Strong | Depends on specific implementation; tightly coupled |
  | Weak | Depends only on abstract interface; loosely coupled |
endlegend
@enduml
